	(82,16,'Quality Assurance Tester (01 post)','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Work with IT Business Analyst, Development and Business team to create test case/scenario.</li>\r\n<li>Review and analyze system specifications.</li>\r\n<li>Execute test cases (manual or automated) and analyze results.</li>\r\n<li>Evaluate process flow according to technical specification.</li>\r\n<li>Create logs to document testing phases and defects.</li>\r\n<li>Carry out regression testing every time when changes are made to the code to fix defects.</li>\r\n<li>Report bugs and errors to Business Analyst and development team.</li>\r\n<li>Help to troubleshoot issue.</li>\r\n<li>Conduct post-release/ post-implementation testing.</li>\r\n<li>Work with cross-functional teams to ensure quality throughout the software development lifecycle.</li>\r\n<li>Liaise with cross-functional team to create user manual and training manual.</li>\r\n<li>Conduct training to end users.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree in IT, Banking or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>A minimum of 3 years experience as QA Tester or a.</li>\r\n<li>Organizational and Analytical skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to document and troubleshoot errors.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to build an automated testing script process and create scripts.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively as a team member and independently.</li>\r\n<li>Experience creating QA test execution strategies, test plans, test cases, test scripts, updating test matrices and release notes and estimating testing efforts.</li>\r\n<li>Competency in Microsoft applications including Word, Excel, and Outlook, Viso, Project, Planner. Knowledge in Office 365 is advantage.</li>\r\n<li>Experince creating training material and conduct training.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to act quickly in a crisis situation to make decisions and keep key stakeholders informed of the situation.</li>\r\n<li>Good spoken and written English.</li>\r\n<li>Good integrity, positive attitude, h