	(272,15,'Deputy Director of Non Credit Product Development Department - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Formulate strategies and implement tactical plans for deposit products and other banking services.</li>\r\n<li>Dealing and leading the product and process development, enhancement, monitoring of non-credit products.</li>\r\n<li>Develop the product policy, procedures, and guideline and process workflows.</li>\r\n<li>Monitor the performance of the products and propose to enhance those existing product lines to be better in the market.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure product price competitiveness and feature benefit suitability to meet needs of our target customer segments.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare business proposals for seeking validation from senior management.</li>\r\n<li>Analyzes cost &amp; benefit of non-credit products, marketing or sale activities.</li>\r\n<li>Prepares the budget plan/sale projections for non-credit product launch, sale or marketing campaign.</li>\r\n<li>Perform other tasks assigned by supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Master degree in banking/finance or business management, or related fields</li>\r\n<li>At least 04 year experience in consumer banking, insurance or financial services industry.</li>\r\n<li>Extensive knowledge in insurance, strong analytical, quantitative, problem solving, communication (written and verbal), presentation, relationship management skills, project management skill.</li>\r\n<li>Be proficient in English both speaking and writing</li>\r\n<li>Be Innovative, dynamic and confident</li>\r\n<li>Be well time management.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,36,15,'1','07/18/2018',0,NULL,8,5,5,'English','2018-07-01 11:13:04','2018-07-01 11:13:04'),
