	(335,15,'Internal Audit Assurance Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review internal auditor&rsquo; work based on the annual plan.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Plan for reviewing the internal auditors&rsquo; work on monthly basis.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform testing on internal audit&rsquo;s working to ensure they follow internal audit policy and manual.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review the internal audit reports, the internal auditor&rsquo;s working papers and the supporting documents.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Prepare an audit assurance working and ensure that all working papers are properly documented and filed.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Find on audit work with proper root cause and recommendation to audit department and branch offices.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks as assigned by supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in accounting or equivalent degree is required.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">At least 1 year working experiences in finance accounting or banking sectors.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good interpersonal, communication and management skills including.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Demonstrate high level of ethical commitments and trustworthiness.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good at communication skills, including English speaking and writing skills.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Computer literate in MS Word, Excel, Power point, and internet Email.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ability to work under pressure highly self-motivated.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Be available to travel to province.<span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong></strong></span></span></span></span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Location</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"bodytext\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400;\">Head Office, Phnom Penh</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,77,15,'1','08/20/2018',0,NULL,3,5,11,'English','2018-08-08 16:35:26','2018-08-08 16:35:26'),
