	(343,19,'Branch Credit Admin Officer - 09 post','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Review Loan Document from Credit Officer before submit to Branch Manager and checking CBC.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Check Client Credit History in CBC by follow the policy and procedure.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Prepare and review loan document before submit Credit Committee.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Review and re-check Loan Agreement, Hypothec Agreement, legal document, and Collateral/Security Documents before giving to customer to process with authority, disbursement, and filing.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Controlling and monitoring Credit Committee Loan minute approving which send by Senior SME Lending Support at Head Office.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Help Branch Manager to share Memo, guideline, and follow up with users to ensure that they are compliance.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Maintain customer information confidentiality.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Recording and tracking client&rsquo;s Collateral information into core banking system.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Safe keeping all client&rsquo;s documents such as Client Information, Loan Document, and Collateral/Security Document by following policy and procedure.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Coordinate related works with Credit Admin Office at Head Office.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Others task as assign by supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Bachelor degree in the field of banking and finance, accounting, economic, law or other equivalent.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">At least 1-year experience in Microfinance/Bank.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Have strong numeric and administrative skill.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Negotiation and internal relationship building.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Sound written and verbal English communication skills.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Advanced Computer Skills (Ms. Word, Excel, and Power Point).</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Ability on problem solving and good communication skills.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Good behavior committed and disciplined\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">013-Po Sen Chey</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">014-Tuol Kouk</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">015-Stueng Mean Chey</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; marg