	(368,15,'Branch Effectiveness Officer for Credit Management​ - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Prepare the Daily performing monitoring Report, Monthly Reports accuracy and timely.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ensure and manage all kinds of credit reports in credit management unit and be capable to work substitutable for others in parallel positions as well.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Make and Verify the Monthly Report on costs of the branch CBC usage checked credit bureau Cambodia service system.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work closely with CBS department to build the all credit reports in branch effectiveness&nbsp; department.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Handle all tasks as required and assigned by direct supervisors and management team.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other task assigned by supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in business administration or related field.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good understanding and knowledge of microfinance and banking sector.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good interpersonal communication, team work and result-oriented.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Computer literacy in MS Offic, Word, Excel, Internet and Email.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good command in English both writing and speaking.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good communication.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Commitment, and Honestly.</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">Head Office (Phnom Penh)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,'1','09/20/2018',0,NULL,3,5,1,'English','2018-08-23 16:45:16','2018-08-23 16:45:16'),
	(369,15,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ១៣១នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">ធ្វើការផ្សាព្វផ្សាយ ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម របស់ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីធីត(HKL) ដើម្បីពង្រីកទីផ្សារ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនសក្តានុពល។</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">រៀបចំឯកសារឥណទាន ដើម្បីផ្តល់ឥណទានជូនអតិថិជន។&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">ត្រួតពិនិត្យ និងតាមដានការសងត្រឡប់របស់អតិថិជន។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">បំពេញការងារផ្សេងៗតាមការចាត់តាំងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">បញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ ឬជានិស្សិតឆ្នាំទី៤ ផ្នែកគ្រប់គ្រងពាណិជ្ជកម្ម ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-sty