	(373,15,'IT Officer for Technical Support - 02 posts','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Provide daily technical support on printer, scanner, email, OS, computer, UPS, AVAYA phone, QMS system, Fingerprint system other hardware and software at Head office and branches</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Support on monitoring of network and data connection lines for all branches, DR, and DC</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Provide maintenance on network equipment in server room at branches, DR, and DC</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Provide support security camera for public ATM </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Supporting on implementation network/server project</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist in doing other assignment required by Manager/Director.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree or engineer in Computer Science</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ability to apply technical standards, principles, theories and techniques</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Knowledge in general of computer hardware and software</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Knowledge on time management and effective planning</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good written and spoken English </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Interested in traveling/ working in the rural area learn or search on the new technology</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Be able to work independent or as team</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24