	(388,28,'Quality Control (Vehicle)','<p><span style=\"color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; text-align: justify;\">Make sure the quality of repair the condition of the vehicle, assist to the service adviser for receiving the customer and carried our interactive inspection, assist to the technician for the quality of repair and fix it first time, supporting promotional activities, monitoring inventory, complying with safety and environment programs and practices, and any other duties as assigned.</span></p>','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; list-style-position: inside; list-style-type: square; line-height: 19.5px; width: 902.391px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;\">Bachelor Degree or higher in Engineering or related field.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;\">Education, training and/or certifications should clearly demonstrate the possession of the knowledge and skills stated above.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;\">High school preferred.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;\">Some college or automotive/vocational training preferred.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,83,15,'1','09/28/2018',1,NULL,8,5,14,'English','2018-08-29 13:46:06','2019-04-18 16:51:16'),
	(389,28,'Service Adviser','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; list-style-position: inside; list-style-type: square; line-height: 19.5px; width: 902.391px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Follow up with customers to ensure they are satisfied with service.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Promote cooperation and teamwork among technicians and support staff.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Assist other Service Advisors when needed.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Check customer\'s service history, schedule appointments, enter repair order information and manage information.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Follow up to resolve and communicate resolution of customer concerns to local market Ford Customer Satisfaction organization.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Verify time ticket information.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; list-style-position: inside; list-style-type: square; line-height: 19.5px; width: 902.391px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Education, training and/or certifications should clearly demonstrate the possession of the knowledge and skills stated above.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Knowledge of automotive is preferable.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Driver&rsquo;s license.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Good in English communication.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">2 years in an automotive service environment preferred.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Using computer to look up information.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Bending, stretching, lifting, reaching, and climbing.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Utilizing physical and manual dexterity.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Driving a vehicle (if properly licensed).</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Lifting up to 50 lbs.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Working Conditions: Noise, Vibration, Paint, Dust, Exhaust fumes, Other hazardous and non-hazardous materials.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,83,15,'1','09/28/2018',1,4,12,5,2,'English','2018-08-29 13:50:21','2019-04-19 08:15:00'),
	(390,28,'Lending Officer','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; list-style-position: inside; list-style-type: square; line-height: 19.5px; width: 902.391px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Update weekly report about cash flow forecast, prospect, and influencer, and monthly planning.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Competitors survey every 3 months on each products (Car, Tractor, HED, Forklifit) and financial institutions and send report to Head of Credit Sales.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Be willing to follow and adapt your supervisor&rsquo;s advice/teaching/request.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Send aged receivable report to Senior Collection Office every Friday afternoon.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Be willing to help and support team when they are busy or on leave.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Teach, support, and train the sales of dealer (Ford, HED, JD, JLR, SP&hellip;) about financing services.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; list-style-position: inside; list-style-type: square; line-height: 19.5px; width: 902.391px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Bachelor Degree of economics, finance and banking, business and other related fields.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Strong knowledge about sales/marketing and credit.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Strong Communication skills.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Willing to work under pressure.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Highest level of business ethics.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Good in English both speaking and writing.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,'1','09/07/2018',1,NULL,3,5,11,'English','2018-08-30 09:20:39','2019-04-18 16:51:13'),
	(391,13,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ៤៥នាក់','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">សិក្សា អនុវត្ថឱ្យត្រឹមត្រូវ និងទាន់សម័យ តាមគោលការណ៍ និងនីតិវិធីឥណទាន។</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">ចុះផ្សព្វផ្សាយ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនគោលដៅ ឱ្យមកប្រើប្រាស់សេវាកម្មហិរញ្ញវត្ថុរបស់ហ្វូណន។</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt;\">សិក្សា វិភាគ និងវាយតម្លៃឥណទាន ឱ្យបានត្រឹមត្រូវ ច្បាស់លាស់ និងមានប្រសិទ្ធភាពខ្ពស់។</span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt;\">តាមដានការប្រើប្រាស់ទុន និងការសងត្រឡប់របស់អតិថិជន។</span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt;\">ធ្វើកិច្ចការផ្សេងៗទៀតតាមតម្រូវការរបស់ថ្នាក់ដឹកនាំ។</span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">បញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញបត្រ ឬកំពុងសិក្សាឆ្នាំទី៣ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រងទូទៅ ឬជំនាញដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">មានបទពិសោធន៍ផ្នែកលក់ ឬផ្នែកទីផ្សារកាន់តែ​ប្រសើរ</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">មានជំនាញក្នុងការប្រាស្រ័យទាក់ទង</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">ជាមនុស្សអំណត់ តស៊ូ ស្វាហាប់ ស្មោះត្រង់ មានឆន្ទៈខ្ពស់ និងមានចំណូលចិត្តបម្រើការងារនៅតាមជនបទ</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួន</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">ផ្តល់អាទិភាពចំពោះបេក្ខជនដែលរស់នៅទីតាំងសុំបម្រើការងារ</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">សាខាខេត្តស្វាយរៀង (០៣), សាខាខេត្តព្រៃវែង (០២), សាខាស្រុកឆ្លូង (០១), សាខាស្រុកឈូក (០១), សាខាខេត្តកំពង់ចាម (០៥), សាខាស្រុកក្រគរ​ (០១), សាខាស្រុកបាធាយ (០១), សាខាខេត្តតាកែវ (០៥), សាខាខេត្តបាត់ដំបង (០៥), សាខាស្រុកជីក្រែង (០១), សាខាស្រុកក្រឡាញ់ (០៣), សាខាខេត្តកំពត (០៣), សាខាខេត្តស្ទឹងត្រែង (០១), សាខាស្រុកកោះធំ (០១), សាខាខេត្តព្រះសីហនុ (០២), និងសាខាក្នុងរាជធានីភ្នំពេញ (១០)</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,'45','09/07/2018',0,NULL,3,5,1,'English','2018-08-31 10:06:43','2018-08-31 10:06:43'),
	(392,15,'System Operation Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Daily control and monitor of business databases, OS, and Storage.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Backup business databases to physical storage and to tape library for monthly basic.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Cooperation in IT technical, operation, and finance team.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Clear daily transactions in system with relevant business support team and report on database performance status.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Monitor archive space and disk space on database servers and storage.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Check, analyses event logs, and report on critical event on business applications.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Backup before running End of Day Process (EOD) on banking system.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work with support team to resolve the error related to core banking system, OS, or storage, and backup data in storage.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Performance other taste assigned by supervisor.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree or 4th year engineer in Computer Science or related field.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">At least have basic knowledge on Linux, UNIX and Oracle database</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Basic of SQL language is preferable</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Knowledge on some business applications is a plus</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Be patient and work commitment.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good written and spoken English.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Be able to work at night shifts.</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">Head Office (Phnom Penh)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,'1','09/18/2018',1,5,7,5,9,'English','2018-09-09 08:36:31','2019-09-23 09:30:07'),
	(393,15,'បេឡាករ (Teller) - ០៤ នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ធ្វើប្រតិបត្តិការសាច់ប្រាក់ប្រចាំថ្ងៃរួមមានបើកប្រាក់កម្ចី ទទួលប្រាក់សំណង និងថែរក្សាសាច់ប្រាក់ក្នុងទូដែក។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">កត់ត្រាប្រតិបត្តិការចំណូល-ចំណាយប្រចាំថ្ងៃចូលក្នុងប្រព័ន្ធ Flexcube</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">កត់ត្រានិងថែរក្សាសៀវភៅបេឡាសក្ខីប័ណ្ណចំណូលចំណាយ និងឯកសារ កម្ចីផ្សេងៗ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ព្យាករណ៍តម្រូវការសាច់ប្រាក់នៅការិយាល័យសាខា និងសាខារង។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">រក្សាព័ត៌មានផ្សេងៗទៀតដែលទាក់ទងនឹងសាច់ប្រាក់និងអនុវត្តការងារផ្សេងៗ ទៀតតាមការណែនាំរបស់អ្នកគ្រប់គ្រង។</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ជានិសិ្សតកំពុងសិក្សារឺបញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រផ្នែកគ្រប់គ្រងពាណិជ្ជកម្ម ឬ ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានអត្តចរិកល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់&nbsp; ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់&nbsp; សុភាពរាបសារ និងមានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms.</span></span><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><strong></strong></span></font></span></span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">សាខាស្រុកបាកាន</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">សាខាស្រុករវៀង</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">សាខាស្រុករមាសហែក</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">សាខាស្រុកទ្រាំង</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,'4','09/15/2018',1,2,3,5,1,'English','2018-09-09 08:40:42','2019-09-24 15:45:07'),
	(394,15,'មន្រ្តីលទ្ធកម្ម (Procurement Officer) - ០១នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">គ្រប់គ្រងសំណើសុំសម្ភារៈរបស់សាខា ទៅតាមការិយាល័យប្រតិបត្តិការដែលបានបែងចែកអោយបានច្បាស់លាស់។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">គ្រប់គ្រង និងរៀបចំ Purchase Request អោយបានត្រឹមត្រូវ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">រៀបចំសំណើទិញសម្ភារៈយោងតាមសំណើជួសជុលអោយបានច្បាស់លាស់។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">រៀបចំចាត់ចែងបោះពុម្ភសៀវភៅគោលការណ៍ពីគ្រប់ផ្នែកដែលស្នើសុំ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ស្វែងរក Quote អោយមានប្រសិទ្ធភាពនិងអនុលោមទៅតាមគោលការណ៍របស់ក្រុមហ៊ុន។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">រៀបចំ Purchase Order ទៅអ្នកផ្គត់ផ្គង់ទៅតាមស្តុកជាក់ស្តែងលើការអនុម័តនិងទូទាត់ការចំណាយជូនអ្នកផ្គត់ផ្គង់អោយបានទាន់ពេល។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ត្រួតពិនិត្យរបាយការណ៍ស្តុកជាមួយអ្នកផ្គត់ផ្គង់អោយបានទៀងទាត់។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ធ្វើកិច្ចការផ្សេងៗទៀត តាមការចាត់តាំងរបស់អ្នកគ្រប់គ្រង។&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">បញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ​ ឬជានិស្សិតកំពុងសិក្សាឆ្នាំទី៤ ផ្នែក គណនេយ្យ, រដ្ឋបាល, ធនាគារ និង ហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ&nbsp; ឬសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានអត្តចរិកល្អ&nbsp;&nbsp; មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់&nbsp; ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់&nbsp; សុភាពរាបសារ និង មានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office (Word &amp; Excel) Internet &amp; Email។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">អាចធ្វើដំណើរបំពេញការងារតាមបណ្តាខេត្ត/ក្រុងនានា។</span></span><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><strong></strong></span></font></span></span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">Head Office (Phnom Penh)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,'1','09/15/2018',1,6,3,5,1,'English','2018-09-09 08:43:49','2019-11-11 14:07:07'),
	(395,15,'Operational Risk Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Coordinate the implementation plan with key relevant stakeholder to proactively in identifying operational risk incidents and potential risks that are relevant.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist risk owner on how to manage operational risks in accordance with operational risk policies procedure and create strategies for solution to response the operational risk incidents.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Involve with the relevant business unit to conduct the risk assessment on new business initiative/service/policy procedure and product development&hellip;etc.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Maintain the recording mechanism of the operational risk register, risk incident report register, operational loss event database and fraud control plan register.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist the Head of Operational Risk Unit to produce the dashboard design and business continuity planning for managing the unexpected risk event that could impact to the business operation of HKL.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks as assigned by direct supervisor/management team.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree of Management, Banking and Finance, Economics, or other related field, English degree is preferable.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">At least 1 year experience on operational risks and fraud risk management.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good understanding and knowledge of loan assessment process in advance.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Self-motivation and able to manage own workload.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work experience in Banking and Finance institute or Operational management.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Be flexible with working hours.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Computer literacy in MS Office includes Word, Excel, Power Point, Internet and Email.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good communication in Khmer and English.<span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong></strong></span></span></span></span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">Head Office (Phnom Penh)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,'1','09/20/2018',1,1,3,5,11,'English','2018-09-09 08:46:54','2019-09-05 05:11:42'),
	(396,15,'មន្រ្តីរដ្ឋបាល (Administrative Officer) - ០១នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">គ្រប់គ្រងឯកសារបុគ្គលិក ឯកសារឥណទាន ឯកសារប្រាក់បញ្ញើសន្សំនិង ឯកសារទ្រព្យតម្កល់ធានា។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">គ្រប់គ្រង និង រៀបចំការិយាល័យ កិច្ចប្រជុំ កំណត់ត្រា របាយការណ៍ប្រជុំ និង ពិធីការផ្សេងៗ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">គ្រប់គ្រងការងារលទ្ធកម្ម និង ការគ្រប់គ្រងទ្រព្យ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">គ្រប់គ្រងការងារសនិ្តសុខ សណ្តាប់ធ្នាប់ និង អនាម័យការិយាល័យ</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">គ្រប់គ្រងការងារដឹកជញ្ជូន និង ធ្វើរបាយការណ៍</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">បំពេញកិច្ចការងារផ្សេងៗ ទៀតដែលចាត់តាំងដោយថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង។&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ជានិសិ្សតកំពុងសិក្សាឬបញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ&nbsp; ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រង រដ្ឋបាលទូទៅ ឬសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានបទពិសោធន៍លើការងារ រដ្ឋបាល កាន់តែប្រសើរ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានជំនាញក្នុងការគ្រប់គ្រង ដោះស្រាយបញ្ហា និងការប្រាស្រ័យទាក់ទងល្អ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានសមត្ថភាព ផ្នែភាសាអង់គ្លេស ទាំងការនិយាយ និងសរសេរ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានសមត្ថភាពផ្នែកកុំព្យូទ័រ លើកម្មវិធី Ms. Word, Ms. Excel, &nbsp;<br />Internet និង Email។&nbsp;</span></span><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><strong></strong></span></font></span></span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">សាខាស្រុកឈូក</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,'1','09/15/2018',1,1,3,5,1,'English','2018-09-09 08:49:24','2019-09-23 08:23:40'),
	(397,15,'គណនេយ្យករ (Accountant) - ០៤នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ធ្វើប្រតិបត្តិការប្រព័ន្ធ Flexcube ដែលរួមមាន ការងារគណនេយ្យ និងគ្រប់គ្រងព័ត៌មានរបស់ការិយាល័យសាខា។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">រក្សាទិន្នន័យ និង កត់ត្រារាល់ប្រតិបត្តិការហិរញ្ញវត្ថុក្នុងប្រព័ន្ធ Flexcube។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ត្រួតពិនិត្យលើរាល់ឯកសារកម្ចី ផ្តល់ព័ត៌មាន និងបញ្ចូលទិន្នន័យទៅក្នុងប្រព័ន្ធ Flexcube។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ត្រួតពិនិត្យសមតុល្យសាច់ប្រាក់ក្នុងបញ្ជី និងរាប់សាច់ប្រាក់ជាប្រចាំថ្ងៃ។ </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">សម្របសម្រួលប្រតិបត្តិការដកប្រាក់ ដាក់ប្រាក់ និងរៀបចំតារាងផ្ទៀងផ្ទាត់ប្រចាំខែ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ត្រួតពិនិត្យចំណូលចំណាយប្រចាំថ្ងៃមុនចុះបញ្ជី និងរក្សាទុកឯកសារយោងផ្សេងៗ និងធ្វើរបាយការណ៍ជូនអ្នកគ្រប់គ្រង។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ធ្វើកិច្ចការផ្សេងៗទៀតតាមការចាត់ណែនាំរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">បញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ ឬជានិស្សិតឆ្នាំទី៤ ផ្នែកគ្រប់គ្រងពាណិជ្ជកម្ម ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានអត្តចរិកល្អ&nbsp;&nbsp; មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់&nbsp; ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសារ និងមានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office <br />(Word &amp; Excel) Internet &amp; Email ។&nbsp;</span></span></span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">សាខាស្រុកឈ្នួល-ឃុំស្នួល</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">សាខាស្រុកក្រគរ-ឃុំឈើតុំ</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">សាខាស្រុកស៊ីធរកណ្តាល-ឃុំព្រែកចង្រ្កាន</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">សាខាស្រុកប្រាសាទបល្ល័ង្គ-ឃុំសាលាវិស័យ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,'4','09/20/2018',1,3,3,5,1,'English','2018-09-09 08:53:39','2019-11-11 14:02:33'),
	(398,15,'Business Application Development ​Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Manage and facilitate programmers to support end users or business team for new request.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Maintain and Follow up to issues from log of application system.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Design process flow and table structures and submit for approval before writing codes and interface. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Design develops tools and reports, and analytical data structures.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ensure BI reports smoothly running an d supporting to end users.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Sharing common practices and experiences to subordinators for knowledge improvement.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Supported&nbsp; and maintain business applications and system</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ensure the issues of running internal application system must be mitigated.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Performance other task assigned by supervisor.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree or engineer in Computer Science.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ability to apply technical standards, principles, theories and techniques for software development.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Some experience programming and development of any application.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Knowledge in programming languages such as VB.Net, ASP.NET, Java, PHP, &hellip;</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Basic Knowledge on MS SQL Server or Oracle Database</span></